<title type="html"><![CDATA[10/17(Sat.)Coronavirus: Ad sticks middle finger to rule breakers/The cyborgs use brain waves to power up muscles(Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=437&amp;p=455#p455"><![CDATA[
10/17(Sat.)<br />Article1: Coronavirus: Berlin ad sticks middle finger to mask rule breakers<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54537519">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54537519</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. What do you think after reading the article?<br />2. What is the main reason why most people in Taiwan are willing to wear a mask?<br />3. What impact do you think this ad will have?<br /><br />Article2: The wearable cyborgs that use brain waves to power up your muscles<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/18/health/japan-cyberdyne-brain-wave-exoskeleton-wellness-scn-hnk-intl/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/18/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion:<br />1. What do you think after reading the article?<br />2. Who needs the device? Please share with your partner.<br />3. What impact do you think this device will have?<br /><br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Oct 14, 2020 11:34 pm</p><hr />
